message.body: ################I miss you face... and your brains. Really I just miss the whole of you. I'm sorry I haven't made the time to see you more and I would like that to change. Any nights you're free for belated birthday dinner?
I miss you too. A lot. How about next Tuesday or Thursday?
Thursday might work. Let me check with my dog trainer and see if he can keep ###### a little late that night.
